name: Coniunctio by Christian Rex van Minnen

metadata.name: Google Antibodies and the Golden Antigen
metadata.description:
'Google Antibodies and the Golden Antigen' is an edition of 51 NFTs featuring an animated version of Christian Rex Van Minnen's painting from the May 2021 exhibit Nature Morte at The Hole Gallery in NYC.

This edition is available exclusively to Van Minion Genesis 1/1 holders. Please visit vanminion.fun to claim. Each Van Minion Genesis piece (51 in total) grants the ability to claim an NFT from this edition.
